.TH LOOTSHEET-NOTES-SEARCH 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-notes-search \\- Search notes by title or body content
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet notes search [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Subcommand: notes search

Search notes by title or body content.

Flags:
  --query   search query (required)

Examples:
  lootsheet notes search --query "Session"
  lootsheet notes search --query "Mayor Elra"
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-h, --help
help for search
.TP
--query=string
search query (required) (default: )
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-notes(1)
